These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, lemonade, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, singing, reading, card-games
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person who's hobby is singing and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | water         | juice   | lemonade | cola       |
| Hobby      | card-games | puzzles | reading   | singing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, scientific, thriller, martial-arts
There are 4 different nationalities: british, colombian, dutch, turkish
1. the turkish is between the person watching thriller movies and the colombian##2
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
3. the dutch is on the right of the british##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Movie-Genre         | scientific | adventure | thriller | martial-arts |
| Nationality   | colombian    | turkish   | british | dutch       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, folk, rock, r&b
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, british, colombian, french
1. the colombian is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
2. the colombian is between the british and the fan of folk##2
3. the british is on the far left##1
4. the french is on the left of the fan of rock##1
5. the fan of folk is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre          | r&b    | electronic | folk   | rock  |
| Nationality   | british | colombian   | french | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, pony, rat
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, ebony, green, azure
1. the person who likes ebony is the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the cat is between the person who likes mauve and the owner of the rat##2
3. the person who likes ebony is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who likes green##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Pet     | rat   | cat    | pony       | lizard   |
| Color   | green | azure | mauve | ebony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, goat, horse, hamster
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, dancing, magic-tricks, skydiving
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the hamster is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is dancing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Pet   | fish        | horse | hamster  | goat |
| Hobby      | magic-tricks | dancing  | skydiving | card-games    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, horse, frog, fish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, parkour, rowing, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the owner of the fish is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the owner of the fish is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the horse is the person who's sport is cycling##1
5. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the horse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Pet   | horse     | frog           | rabbit | fish  |
| Sport         | cycling | skateboarding | parkour   | rowing |

