.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, iced-tea, coffee
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, roller, snowmobile
1. the person drinking tea is the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person driving the bus and the person drinking iced-tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | coffee   | tea | hot-chocolate | iced-tea      |
| Transport     | roller | bus    | motorbike  | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, singing, card-games, magic-tricks
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, snowmobile
1. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person driving the roller##2
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby       | board-games | magic-tricks | card-games     | singing   |
| Transport   | roller   | motorbike     | snowmobile | helicopter |

