.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
There 4 different types of food: pepper, papaya, asparagus, watermelon
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, scooter, ship, van
1. the person eating asparagus is between the person driving the boat and the person eating pepper##2
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
3. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the van##1
5. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Food         | papaya | asparagus | pepper | watermelon |
| Transport   | boat         | van       | scooter    | ship         |

