.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, garlic, peach, plum
4 different pets are kept: hamster, fish, snake, lizard
1. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person eating plum##1
2. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person eating peach##1
3. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
4. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
5. the owner of the fish is between the person eating garlic and the owner of the lizard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | plum   | peach      | garlic   | avocado  |
| Pet   | lizard | fish | snake | hamster |

