.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
City: boston, liverpool, miami, hannover
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, pop, punk, trance
1. the fan of punk is the person traveling to liverpool##1
2. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of trance##1
3. the fan of gospel is the person traveling to boston##1
4. the person traveling to miami is the fan of pop##1
5. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
6. the fan of pop is between the person traveling to liverpool and the person traveling to hannover##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| City         | liverpool | miami | hannover | boston |
| Music-Genre   | punk          | pop     | trance  | gospel     |

