2. the police-officer is between the owner of the turtle and the designer##2
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
4. the designer is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | designer | police-officer | musician | nurse     |
| Pet   | dog   | rabbit    | turtle   | hedgehog |

