.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-18::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
House: futuristic, cape-cod, colonial, art-deco
1. the cape-cod house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
2. the futuristic house is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the futuristic house and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
4. the person who's hobby is singing is the futuristic house##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby       | singing | puzzles | rock-climbing | collecting |
| House   | futuristic    | cape-cod  | art-deco    | colonial       |

