.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, australian, chinese, polish
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, techno, funk, gospel
1. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
2. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of techno##1
3. the polish is the fan of ambient##1
4. the fan of gospel is between the american and the chinese##2
5. the chinese is the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | polish   | american   | australian | chinese |
| Music-Genre         | ambient | techno | gospel     | funk    |

